{
  "stem": "3212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I saw-- when we were-- I saw-- I heard the screaming from children, when they threw them in the air.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I heard shooting after them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I went into the crematorium, I saw pieces of meat when they threw the children on the-- on the wall.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Sonderkommando told us they-- they always when they put the people in the gas chambers, they had glass windows they looked through till-- it took probably five to 10 minutes till the last one died.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some people, even, they-- they put in the crematorium alive, when they were-- had a strong heart and they could live it over, they threw them-- threw them in the crematorium alive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there's a lot of things that we were told, before-- there were people that were years in Birkenau and Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That before the crematoriums, they had-- they had, like, walls, and they threw chlorine on the people, different deaths.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were shooting people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there was times when all the five crematoriums were full speed working and still-- still people came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after the crematoriums they had a-- a soccer place-- a-- a size of a soccer place or football place-- that was digged out-- was a big ditch.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on the end of the ditch they had a little-- they had a gas chamber, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the crematoriums were working full, they-- they sent people to the gas chambers and didn't even burn them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They threw them right in the-- in the ditch by the thousands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when it was full, probably, they covered it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I know after the war I went there, and I was digging there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you can find the bones.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
